Curly Square Version History
============================

09/08/12: 1.0 - Initial launch - FC V 0.1

Updated game icons
Fixed iPad Launch icons
Fixed quit button layout error on iPhone
Re-enabled Flurry (doh)
Moved to FCView Lua object
Added leaderboards to iTunes Connect
Fixed some View problems - ads and frame
Turned off FCConnect in release builds
Fixed score bar bug on game win

30/08/12: 1.0.1 - Bug fix

Graphical overhaul

14/09/12: 1.1 - Graphical overhaul

Removed all C++11 datatypes - preparing for Android build
Centralised the platform interface
Rebalanced the scoring weights to reward harder games
Added iPhone5 launch image - enabling 16:9 screen



